{"word":"G1318 - διδακτός - didaktós - did-ak-tos' - Taught","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">διδακτός</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">didaktós</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">did-ak-tos'</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Taught</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Adjective / பெயரடை</span>"},{"paragraph":"போதிக்கிற - பெயரடை"},{"paragraph":"that can be taught,taught, instructed"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>From <a href=\"#/G1321 - διδάσκω - didáskō - did-as'-ko/1321\">G1321</a>; (subjectively) <i>instructed</i> or (objectively) <i>communicated</i> by teaching: - taught, which . . . teacheth.</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>தொடர்புடைய எண்கள் / Cognate: </strong><a href=\"#/G1317/1317\">G1317</a>, <a href=\"#/G1318/1318\">G1318</a>, <a href=\"#/G1319/1319\">G1319</a>, <a href=\"#/G1320/1320\">G1320</a>, <a href=\"#/G1321/1321\">G1321</a>, <a href=\"#/G1322/1322\">G1322</a>, <a href=\"#/G2085/2085\">G2085</a>, <a href=\"#/G2567/2567\">G2567</a>, <a href=\"#/G3547/3547\">G3547</a>, <a href=\"#/G5572/5572\">G5572</a>"}]}